snippet.title: Painted In Blood Summer Showcase Trailer
snippet.description:
If you missed Zlim's event yesterday, here's a new trailer - now Slow-mo is officially a part of core game's mechanics now, also shows couple new things.
Classical music is a conscious choice  :)
